{"tid":2508630,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"免驅逐令只保障房客 加州業主逼遷不成惟有露宿街頭","createTime":"2021-04-29T01:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T02:18:44.000Z","uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7a54d3f6c2fcc7f6971c3545dae093449b481170","tid":2508630,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T01:58:13.000Z","msg":"受到疫情影響，美國不少無法交租的房客可以免被逼遷直至6月底。然而洛杉磯一位房東卻因為免驅逐令，而無法住進自己物業，只能以車為家。<br />\n<br />\n這位不願透露身份的男子向abc7表示，他在南洛杉磯West Adams地區擁有一個複式單位，分租予兩名房客。最近他因為辦理離婚，與妻子分居後，需要有新往所。但由於免驅逐令，他無法要求任何一個房客遷出他的物業好讓他自住。「最令我沮喪的是，市政府建議我入住遊民收容所，即使我在這城市擁有物業。」<br />\n<br />\n他補充表示，雖然房客一直有交租，但他的物業受到租務管制，只能按通脹加租，而且房東亦要花費大筆金錢維護物業，以達到城市的要求，所以出租物業未有為他帶來太多收入。<br />\n<br />\n根據加州於1985年通過的《埃利斯法案》（Ellis Act），受租務管制的物業房東若要驅逐房客，只能因為出售物業﹑將其轉換為共享公寓﹑或讓該物業空置五年。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n熟悉租務的律師海拉皮提安（Victor Hairapetian）建議，在這種情況下，房東其實可以合法地要求房客遷出，條件是要幫助房客搬走，需花費2萬美元以上，如果房東沒有這個搬遷費用，就無計可施<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210429/MPFRPNW3EBBQBOSS66KJ4XFV5Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210429%2FMPFRPNW3EBBQBOSS66KJ4XFV5Y%2F&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzVT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=83c8032d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210429%2FMPFRPNW3EBBQBOSS66KJ4XFV5Y%2F&h=83ea78f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210429/MPFRPNW3EBBQBOSS66KJ4XFV5Y/</a>"},{"pid":"d131f4b4e69f24344a8a69298e2f78f08c4db421","tid":2508630,"uid":77196,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T01:59:12.000Z","msg":"住得果頭就要有大愛呀"},{"pid":"af6b37527da074d3389f184ed280b44c73760b74","tid":2508630,"uid":256837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:00:02.000Z","msg":"加北美都係保障租客，就算唔交租都唔可以趕走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8634692ab9546909fdb0ce8be83d2c803099f0ae","tid":2508630,"uid":270327,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:08:58.000Z","msg":"所以有好多香港人支那人，去到當地大手掃物業，然後諗住好似喺香港咁，放租咪得，反正都係搵人幫手供樓，但係原來出事先至知，當地法律係保障租霸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe99f04d3e88927670e5c32858d356827d6e27e6","tid":2508630,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af6b37527da074d3389f184ed280b44c73760b74","tid":2508630,"uid":256837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:00:02.000Z","msg":"加北美都係保障租客，就算唔交租都唔可以趕走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:11:36.000Z","msg":"咁業主仲可以點做?"},{"pid":"5a7d6fc49fffd5b2ff17bab97be606d6f4628480","tid":2508630,"uid":116960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d131f4b4e69f24344a8a69298e2f78f08c4db421","tid":2508630,"uid":77196,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T01:59:12.000Z","msg":"住得果頭就要有大愛呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:12:20.000Z","msg":"但其實真係咁先可以壓到樓價,呢個CASE根本RARE到唔係法律漏洞黎,仲要租客有交租"},{"pid":"03b45d6a05d4492255c838d77a951a8714d2628e","tid":2508630,"uid":57073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:13:12.000Z","msg":"咁人地有交租 唔通你業主大鳩晒<br />\n一句話自己住返就拎咩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a90bd7d898f959e8a3987adf9e22e852a4cbd4","tid":2508630,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:14:51.000Z","msg":"香港幾時跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90c7351abeec02c30ce4ec3034d8113b93caf47a","tid":2508630,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:15:12.000Z","msg":"點解加洲啲屋仲可以咁撚貴"},{"pid":"cdac9215be96322feb80b3adf59d2fafa6623f85","tid":2508630,"uid":256837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"